<h1>Accessibility for Authors</h1>
<p>Authors and content creators are essential to making information accessible to everyone. Your writing and formatting choices can help all users understand and engage with your content.</p>

<h2>How Authors Support Accessibility</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Use clear, simple language and avoid jargon.</li>
  <li>Structure content with headings, lists, and short paragraphs.</li>
  <li>Provide descriptive text for links and images (alt text).</li>
  <li>Ensure documents and web pages are readable by screen readers.</li>
  <li>Use accessible document formats (e.g., tagged PDFs, semantic HTML).</li>
</ul>

